ium produced in small colliding systems.\nThis finding supports the idea that multi-differential measurements, such as\nthose based on event categorization according to multiplicity and spherocity,\nare useful to study final-state observables in ultrarelativistic proton-nucleus\ncollisions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2022 17:37:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Oct 2022 14:02:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-13"}
