ermines the\nlongitudinal component of the two-photon-two-fermion irreducible vertex, while\nit is proposed to use the Dyson-Schwinger equation to determine the transverse\npart of this irreducible diagram. The contribution of this irreducible vertex\nto a low-energy effective photon-fermion vertex is discussed and the fermionic\noperators that are generated are computed in terms of the fermion propagator\nfunctions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2022 17:46:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Jan 2023 08:21:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-06"}
