 the pressure range of 1 bar -- 0.1\nmbar across various metallicities and carbon-to-oxygen (C/O) ratios. The small\nscale of the mini-chemical scheme permits simple use and fast computation,\nwhich is optimal for implementation in a 3D GCM or a retrieval framework. We\nfocus on the thermochemical kinetics of net reactions in this paper and address\nphotochemistry in a follow-up paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2022 17:54:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-10"}
