AR and MWA, the ionosphere\nover the GMRT is more active, which is expected due to its location near the\nmagnetic equator.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2022 18:00:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-12"}
