l trajectories of the associated mean field control\nproblem are unique for almost every starting point, for a suitable probability\nmeasure on the space of probability measures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2022 22:20:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Jun 2022 09:14:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-30"}
