omated\nperformance testing framework developed for this code base using a changepoint\ndetection method. The framework is used to make actionable decisions about\nperformance within MALI. We provide several concrete examples of scenarios in\nwhich the framework has identified performance regressions, improvements, and\nalgorithm differences over the course of two years of development.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2022 23:09:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-12"}
